
Overview of noun harrier

The noun harrier has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                      
1. harasser, harrier -- (a persistent attacker; "the harassers were not members of the regular army")
2. harrier -- (a hound that resembles a foxhound but is smaller; used to hunt rabbits)
3. harrier -- (hawks that hunt over meadows and marshes and prey on small terrestrial animals)
